Local checklist
- Lint clean: `bun run lint`.
- Typecheck: `bun run typecheck`.
- Tests green: `bun test` (or `bun run test`).
- Build passes: `bun run build`.

PR requirements
- Link issue/ticket.
- Include screenshots for UI changes.
- No new warnings in console during e2e smoke.
